{
  "stem": "5639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father perished 10 days before the end of the war, because he was such a believer in German integrity that all-- he was on a death march.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people around him said, go, let's run away and save myself-- save ourselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not him.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, they told us to march.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they find us, they will kill us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the middle of winter he marched, and he felt-- he fell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And either he was left there to freeze to death, or a German bullet finished him off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was, in this part of Poland, it was about 10 days before the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when did that place, what date-- not what date exactly, but what month?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I reconstructed that it could have been in February '45.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that part of Poland was already freed but the Russians in February.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So therefore-- so, you see, therefore this also is very important for all our testimonies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can say that I probably have forgotten a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I probably cannot address some of my memories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I also am sure that I don't edit any of my memories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which is a very important thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I might choose not-- perhaps not I might choose, but it has chosen not to be dealt with yet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot address my stay in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My Auschwitz experience is on a-- I came to Auschwitz after Annaburg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I told you, there was the Judenrein and eventually in '44 I went to that labor camp Annaburg.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from Annaburg-",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Annaburg during the attempt on Hitler's life, which was in July-- 20th of July I think, '44.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which means I wasn't there very long.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
